description: I. Letter dated 12/01/2009 from John Hutton MP to James Arbuthnot MP regarding the legal basis for a UK military presence in Iraq in 2009. 2 p. II. Council of Ministers resolution 439 dated 16/12/2008 regarding the law for withdrawal of forces from Iraq. 2 p. III. Council of Representatives resolution 50 dated 23/12/2008 regarding withdrawal of forces from Iraq. 1 p. IV. Memorandum of Understanding dated 01/01/2009 between the UK and Iraq regarding the withdrawal of forces from Iraq. 3 p.
